tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: Dr. Barjinder is superb, since I was not able to move properly so was hesitant to go to the Clinic and took the consultation over a Video Call through Practo however since we were not able to determine the exact issue and since I was a bit sceptical if there was Bone broken or a Severe Muscle Sprain, Dr. Barjinder asked me to come to the clinic to clear all my doubts, At the Clinic he did all his diagnoses and I got an X-Ray done but by God’s Grace it was only a Muscle issue and not a Bone issue, Then he calmly explained all the steps of what to do and what not to do. Dr. Barjinder is the most Calm and Composed Doctor I have met, I have a phobia for Doctors wherein they won’t listen and would tell you to do something which you might not be comfortable in but with Dr. Barjinder it was totally opposite. “The Best Doctor “ also the Staff was very friendly at the clinic and got all my medicines and Rib Brace at the same place. Highly Recommended!!
Doctor is v good and treatment to v good and doctor is near my location and my house  .he is v good doctor orthopaedic

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
I am senior female over 70, suffering Long back. Could not manage to improve my health problem. It is my first visit. Very much satisfied with the attending Doctor, Barjinder Singh ji. Also received all required services like xray, Pathology, bone density test, and physio therapy etc. all at one point. I really appreciate the most satisfying experience and interaction with the doctor and possible and reasonable time consuming event. Final results may come later on in due course and I hope the good results.
 I give my blessings and prayers with good wishes for the said AMRIT Clinic.

tags: Treatment satisfaction,Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Value for money,
review:
*** **** ***** ******* * **** **** *** **** ** ******I am a teacher and I distinctly remember my students had their exams of 12th board. Accidentally my ankle got fractured and I was rushed to nearby hospital. To my disappointment I was advised immediate surgery.Thankfully someone recommended saying that second opinion must be taken .I went to Dr Barjinder and he said that no surgery was required only treatment like my leg needs a plaster for few weeks.An assurance was given that I would walk again on my feet as I did earlier whereas the Dr who advised surgery didn't guarantee. Left with little choice I went with Amrit clinic and within 8 weeks I was running like I did earlier. 
What else could one ask for .He saved me from surgery and ofcourse from shelling surgery money.
God bless him
reply_text:
It was nice to hear about your complete recovery fro fracture of ankle, without surgery.
May god keep you in good health.

review:
** ** **** ************* ** *** *** **** **** ** ***** *********** *******. My son was told for surgery for fracture in his hand. I came for second opinion. Dr. Birendra fixed it without operation. 
I highly recommend him.
Got the right treatment at right time. Recommend him for his skills and right guidance more over his friendly nature

Doctor was very polite and listened to the problems very patiently. The diagnosis was properly explained and treatment started with medicines and physiotherapy. The facility of x-rays and physiotherapy at one place and efficient staff made the experience very smooth and quick.

My knee was giving lot of pain. I was having difficulty in walking. Doctor examined my knee joint and diagnosed as advanced stage of osteoarthritis. I was given injection in knee joint and my pain decreased. I had come two years ago for pain in other knee, which was better with injection.
I am fully satisfied with the treatment.

This was my first visit to this clinic. The doctor was very polite. I was advised x-ray and bone density testing. I was not carrying enough cash, but still doctor allowed me to get the tests done and pay the remaining amount later. This kind of gesture is hard to find these days.

My appointment started in time. The doctor was very friendly and soft spoken. He listened to the complaints and examined thoroughly. I was started on physiotherapy and medication. The presence of x-rays, bone density and physiotherapy at one place made the whole experience very fast and pleasant.

I had pain in right elbow following fall, about 2 weeks ago. The doctor examined and got x-ray done and diagnosed the fracture in elbow and promptly applied plaster. My pain was reduced and everything was done very quickly. The staff was very efficient.

I had came for pain and stiffness of shoulder joint. After listening to my complaints and examining, doctor gave diagnosis of frozen shoulder. I was started on physiotherapy and medications. Last year I had came for my backache problem, which was completely cured after simple medicines and physiotherapy. I had complete trust in his diagnosis and treatment.

I had swelling of knees and difficulty in walking since years. The doctor removed the excess fluid from my knees under local anaesthesia. My pain and swelling decreased immediately. I was able to walk comfortably. I am very satisfied with the treatment.

The doctor listened to the complaints patiently and thoroughly examined. After getting x-rays done, he explained the diagnosis and started me on physiotherapy and medications. *** ********* *** **** ********* ** * **** **** ****** **** ***** **** ******

I was treated by plaster application for 5 weeks for fracture of left ankle. The plaster was so comfortable that I was able to walk without pain and do my routine works. I am completely normal now. I am really thankful to the doctor *** ********* **********

I had come with fracture of right wrist for which plaster was already applied by some other doctor last week. I had lot of pain and was not able to do any work. The doctor removed the plaster got new x-ray done and applied light weight fibre cast. My pain was relieved and I could use my hand for routine activities. I am fully satisfied with the treatment.

The doctor was very polite and friendly. He listened to the complaints patiently and gave the diagnosis of tennis elbow and carpal tunnel syndrome. *** ********* ** **** ********** We have been coming here since years. I would definitely recommend this doctor to others for any orthopaedic problem.

Doctor was very polite ** ************* *my x rays were promptly done and plaster was applied for fracture I was relived of pain very quickly.all the staff was very helpful all the charges were informed before the start of procedure overall very nice experience.
